            <thetext>When using the playground to demonstrate bugs through test code, one often needs the log window to output debug messages (see for example http://bugzilla.qooxdoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=6406). However, the log window is not opened by default, so when a user clicks on the link to open the playground s/he doesn&#39;t see anything and needs to manually open the log.

Please add an URL hash parameter to save the state of the log window, so that when creating a short URL to use in bug reports/emails/ML, the log window will open by default when it was open when the short URL was created.</thetext>
